Added pipefail to all bash scripts' strict mode.

Updated scripts to use 'set -euo pipefail' instead of 'set -euo' or 'set -eu'.

Affected scripts:
- git-env.sh
- git-mark.sh
- git-pp.sh
- git-stash-drop-range.sh

Note: This may break things in some scripts with pipefail enabled.

/Claude-haiku@4.5
